aries. These correlations are useful to provide estimates\nof the key orbital parameters Porb and e from the Halpha line in future Be\ngamma-ray binary candidates.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 9 Jan 2012 10:20:04 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 21 Mar 2012 16:06:38 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-03"}
